#lem: ma[ship]; u[ride]; sa[move about]
#etcsl: line-id=A.2

3. %e ga-ša-an-ŋen %s abzu-še₃ %e di-da-[ŋu₁₀-ne]
#lem: gašan[lady]N; abzu[(cosmic) underground water]; de[go]
#etcsl: line-id=A.3

4. e₂  %e  {d}mu-ul-lil₂-la₂-še₃  %s  kur₉-ra-[ŋu₁₀-ne]
#lem: e[house]; Mullil[1]DN; kur[enter]
#etcsl: line-id=A.4

5. %e ga-ša-an %s kur-ra dirig-ga %e me-e-[ŋen-na]
#lem: gašan[lady]N; kur[mountain(s)]; dirig[make more than]; meʾe[I]
#etcsl: line-id=A.5

